	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is what i did with my prymary char, the bard:<br>-get banded, bronze helm, boots, gloves and arms.<br>-next step was doing the full lambent armor, started at 23 ended at 37, between those lvls, at 23 i get the elements to make lambent helm, i get blackened armor and still used bronze boots till 31, oh i used banded neck till 35, when i was high enough to camp rygorrs and get 2 orc fang earring and orc neck. im not going to explain the full quest but my order was helm, bracers (both one of then, one thanks to Rondite), gloves, arms, bp, legs and boots, but i get SS boots at 31. Now at 48 im using basically the same, SS boots, hagmans noose or Lambent helm, lambent armor, orc neck, mask of decepcion, 8ac svcold cloak, ac 6 sv6 shoulders, str6 dex6 ring, ch7 dex 5 ring, a great belt from sebilis (name is too long :P),and  hp 10 thing from CC in range slot. About weapon this was my progression: giant militia longsword (someone gave it to me when i was 8), blackened iron sword 10 29 this thing was excellent on those days, lvl 20sh, then i get a SSoY, and stormfeather talon, i have used those wepons, the SSoy an the talons till lvl 47, but one day at lvl 48 i get a Partisan and the the flameweaver (Halloween Evnt) in lake Rathe, just at the zone with Feerott there was a Garg with it waiting for me ! Thats all, send me a /tell if u got any question.<br><br>Jotun Moonshiled &lt;48&gt; Bard of Legacy of Shadows<br>Lanys<br><br>"Who dares, win" or dies trying<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
